# FILE: adminDashboard/adminDashboard.desc
# ROLE: Platform Supreme Control Center
# ROUTE: /admin
# ACCOUNT: Admin only — all other account types get 403 redirect
# THEME: Dark · high-density data · colored alert pills · monospace values

## DESIGN SYSTEM
- LAYOUT: full-width sidebar (240px) + main content area
- SIDEBAR BG: bg-[#0F1828] + border-l border-[#1E2D45]
- MAIN BG: bg-[#070C18]
- ACCENT: gradient-bg buttons · rose for danger actions · emerald for confirmations
- DATA TABLES: bg-[#0F1828] · rounded-2xl · border · monospace for IDs and amounts

## SIDEBAR NAVIGATION
- Admin Overview (index) → /admin
- User Account Manager → /admin/users
- Universal Order Manager → /admin/orders
- Library Manager → /admin/library
- Store Inventory → /admin/inventory
- Revenue Tracker → /admin/revenue
- Ad Console → /admin/ads
- System Config → /admin/config

## DASHBOARD INDEX (Overview)
- STAT CARDS ROW: Total Users · Active Students · Active Business Accounts · Pending Verifications
- QUICK LINKS to most-used tools
- RECENT ACTIVITY LOG: "User #9921 verified." · "New business account pending approval." etc.
- SYSTEM STATUS: green dot "جميع الأنظمة تعمل"

## ACCOUNT TYPE MANAGEMENT
- Admin dashboard shows ALL THREE account types:
  - 🎓 Student accounts (with verification status)
  - 💼 Business accounts (with businessType: vendor/advertiser/freelancer and approval status)
  - 🔐 Admin accounts (internal only, cannot be created via public registration)
- USER TABLE COLUMNS: Name · Account Type · Business Type (if applicable) · Status · XP · Actions
- FILTERS: by accountType · by status · by date

## KEY MANTRA
- "Integrity is the Foundation. Challenge Every Day."
